putting away trash: Congrats that's great! keeps the environment clean (+20), Contributes to pollution (-20), Causes water pollution (-20)
buying groceries: That's great for the environment - keep it up! (+10), Unfortunately this contributes to pollution and causes animals/environment to suffer (-10)
going on a road trip with friends: This is great! carpooling saves use of gas which prevents air pollution (+30), This causes extra emission of fossil fuels into the air contributing heavily to air pollution (-30)
had lunch: This is actually bad for the environment as it can hurt the growth of aquatic organisms (-10), Unfortunately even small acts like these contribute to pollution (-10), This is great! prevents pollution (+10)